{"_id":"3Jw7XIwJ0hcz0DLu","name":"Wyvern","type":"Monster","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/monsters/wyvern.svg","items":[{"_id":"1n8zTWZDxEcRUwWz","name":"Fang","type":"Weapon","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"","isEquipped":true,"type":{"value":"—","choices":{"warlock":{"":"","Casual":"Casual","Martial":"Martial"},"warpstar":{"":"","Small":"Small","Medium":"Medium","Heavy":"Heavy"}}},"damage":{"roll":"2d6","type":{"value":"Piercing","choices":{"warlock":{"":"","Crushing":"Crushing","Piercing":"Piercing","Slashing":"Slashing","Blast":"Blast"},"warpstar":{"":"","Crushing":"Crushing","Piercing":"Piercing","Slashing":"Slashing","Energy":"Energy","Ship":"Ship"}}}},"skill":{"value":"Weapon Skill","choices":{"warlock":{"—":"—","Blunt":"Blunt","Bow":"Bow","Brawling":"Brawling","Crossbow":"Crossbow","Large blade":"Large blade","Pole arm":"Pole arm","Small blade":"Small blade","Thrown":"Thrown"},"warpstar":{"—":"—","Blades":"Blades","Blunt":"Blunt","Brawling":"Brawling","Ship gunner":"Ship gunner","Small arms":"Small arms","Thrown":"Thrown"}}},"activeSystem":"warlock"},"ownership":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}},{"_id":"yYuqhYXeL9HjR3xV","name":"Hide","type":"Armour","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"","isEquipped":true,"type":{"value":"","choices":{"":"","Light":"Light","Modest":"Modest","Heavy":"Heavy"}},"reductionRoll":"1d3"},"ownership":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}},{"_id":"uyUJq3dFIAMc2UbN","name":"Flying","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":"jZ1bx1OgshF0koNu","sort":500000,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.2RsIqNmhzsx9vw6I"}},"system":{"description":"<p>Using wings or similar, this creature can fly. Treat this as normal movement, but ignoring barriers that can be flown over at the game master's discretion. This creature cannot be engaged in melee combat whilst flying unless it chooses to attack, in which case it can be targeted.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.warlock.bestiary-warlock.3Jw7XIwJ0hcz0DLu"}},"system":{"resources":{"actionsPerRound":{"value":2,"max":2},"stamina":{"value":32,"max":32}},"biography":{"description":"<p>A great winged serpent, wyverns hunt over some of the great plains and occasionally drift into the Kingdom. They are large enough to take cattle, and so can cause great destruction. Many a warrior has tested their mettle by hunting down and killing a wyvern before it hatches its eggs.</p>"},"type":"Monster","weaponSkill":7,"adventuringSkills":2,"gear":{"weapons":[],"armour":[],"equipment":[]}},"ownership":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"prototypeToken":{"name":"Wyvern","displayName":0,"actorLink":false,"width":1,"height":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"alpha":1,"light":{"alpha":0.5,"angle":360,"bright":0,"coloration":1,"dim":0,"luminosity":0.5,"saturation":0,"contrast":0,"shadows":0,"animation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5,"reverse":false,"type":null},"darkness":{"min":0,"max":1},"attenuation":0.5,"color":null},"disposition":-1,"displayBars":0,"bar1":{"attribute":null},"bar2":{"attribute":null},"flags":{},"randomImg":false,"texture":{"src":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/monsters/wyvern.svg","scaleX":1,"scaleY":1,"offsetX":0,"offsetY":0,"rotation":0,"tint":null},"sight":{"angle":360,"enabled":false,"range":0,"brightness":1,"color":null,"attenuation":0.1,"saturation":0,"contrast":0,"visionMode":"basic"},"detectionModes":[]},"_stats":{"systemId":"wa