rlock":{"—":"—","Blunt":"Blunt","Bow":"Bow","Brawling":"Brawling","Crossbow":"Crossbow","Large blade":"Large blade","Pole arm":"Pole arm","Small blade":"Small blade","Thrown":"Thrown"},"warpstar":{"—":"—","Blades":"Blades","Blunt":"Blunt","Brawling":"Brawling","Ship gunner":"Ship gunner","Small arms":"Small arms","Thrown":"Thrown"}}},"activeSystem":"warlock"},"ownership":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}},{"_id":"SPORQwArreX4Y7j4","name":"Hide","type":"Armour","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"","isEquipped":true,"type":{"value":"","choices":{"":"","Light":"Light","Modest":"Modest","Heavy":"Heavy"}},"reductionRoll":"1d6"},"ownership":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}},{"_id":"pQYrQCKKBZIorhkg","name":"Intelligent","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":"jZ1bx1OgshF0koNu","sort":-100000,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.viEhV1k2WBxXnAHV"}},"system":{"description":"<p>This being is intelligent, can speak (but perhaps not in a tongue the characters know) and use tools and weapons. It is also able to create strategies and plans.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}},{"_id":"J74ynyL5SR6mND3I","name":"Spell caster","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":"jZ1bx1OgshF0koNu","sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.FOVCFt6tZfXWVBEK"}},"system":{"description":"<p>The being is able to cast spells. The games master should feel free to assign the creature spells that reflect its power. It uses stamina to cast spells and requires an incantation skill check.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.warlock.bestiary-warlock.D25OqZsqi4Or5BfT"}},"system":{"resources":{"actionsPerRound":{"value":4,"max":4},"stamina":{"value":42,"max":42}},"biography":{"description":"<p>Demons come in all shapes and sizes, as this is a catch-all term of otherworldly beings draw to the material world. Here they can feed, and so most will do whatever they can to remain here. Wizards know that most spells are powered by demons, with whom their ancient forebears signed dread pacts in return for sacrifice. It seems most demons believe they got a rough end of that bargain in the end, and are constantly trying to wriggle out of the agreements they made, hence the strict wording of spells and the dire consequences of errors.</p>"},"type":"Otherworldly","weaponSkill":10,"adventuringSkills":6,"gear":{"weapons":[],"armour":[],"equipment":[]}},"ownership":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"prototypeToken":{"name":"Demon","displayName":0,"actorLink":false,"width":1,"height":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"alpha":1,"light":{"alpha":0.5,"angle":360,"bright":0,"coloration":1,"dim":0,"luminosity":0.5,"saturation":0,"contrast":0,"shadows":0,"animation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5,"reverse":false,"type":null},"darkness":{"min":0,"max":1},"attenuation":0.5,"color":null},"disposition":-1,"displayBars":0,"bar1":{"attribute":null},"bar2":{"attribute":null},"flags":{},"randomImg":false,"texture":{"src":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/daemon-skull.svg","scaleX":1,"scaleY":1,"offsetX":0,"offsetY":0,"rotation":0,"tint":null},"sight":{"angle":360,"enabled":false,"range":0,"brightness":1,"color":null,"attenuation":0.1,"saturation":0,"contrast":0,"visionMode":"basic"},"detectionModes":[]},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersi