{"warlock":{"—":"—","Blunt":"Blunt","Bow":"Bow","Brawling":"Brawling","Crossbow":"Crossbow","Large blade":"Large blade","Pole arm":"Pole arm","Small blade":"Small blade","Thrown":"Thrown"},"warpstar":{"—":"—","Blades":"Blades","Blunt":"Blunt","Brawling":"Brawling","Ship gunner":"Ship gunner","Small arms":"Small arms","Thrown":"Thrown"}}},"activeSystem":"warlock"},"ownership":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}},{"_id":"Aw0oOgs0teZi05pN","name":"Hide","type":"Armour","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"","isEquipped":true,"type":{"value":"","choices":{"":"","Light":"Light","Modest":"Modest","Heavy":"Heavy"}},"reductionRoll":"1d6"},"ownership":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}},{"_id":"yarSnlHLEEuHOpeH","name":"Intelligent","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":"jZ1bx1OgshF0koNu","sort":700000,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.viEhV1k2WBxXnAHV"}},"system":{"description":"<p>This being is intelligent, can speak (but perhaps not in a tongue the characters know) and use tools and weapons. It is also able to create strategies and plans.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}},{"_id":"FlCXTv10ss7Yl2wK","name":"Flying","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":"jZ1bx1OgshF0koNu","sort":500000,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.2RsIqNmhzsx9vw6I"}},"system":{"description":"<p>Using wings or similar, this creature can fly. Treat this as normal movement, but ignoring barriers that can be flown over at the game master's discretion. This creature cannot be engaged in melee combat whilst flying unless it chooses to attack, in which case it can be targeted.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.warlock.bestiary-warlock.ExEzWzCubDH4xD7q"}},"system":{"resources":{"actionsPerRound":{"value":3,"max":3},"stamina":{"value":41,"max":41}},"biography":{"description":"<p>A noble beast with the body of a lion, the head and wings of an eagle, griffins are intelligent, sociable beings, and make great company. They have huge appetites however, and so are not often tolerated in civilised lands. It is however as common to see a sage sent to persuade the griffin to move on than it is to see warriors sent to destroy it, which is lucky considering the creature's might.</p>"},"type":"Monster","weaponSkill":8,"adventuringSkills":6,"gear":{"weapons":[],"armour":[],"equipment":[]}},"ownership":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"prototypeToken":{"name":"Griffin","displayName":0,"actorLink":false,"width":1,"height":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"alpha":1,"light":{"alpha":0.5,"angle":360,"bright":0,"coloration":1,"dim":0,"luminosity":0.5,"saturation":0,"contrast":0,"shadows":0,"animation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5,"reverse":false,"type":null},"darkness":{"min":0,"max":1},"attenuation":0.5,"color":null},"disposition":-1,"displayBars":0,"bar1":{"attribute":null},"bar2":{"attribute":null},"flags":{},"randomImg":false,"texture":{"src":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/griffin-symbol.svg","scaleX":1,"scaleY":1,"offsetX":0,"offsetY":0,"rotation":0,"tint":null},"sight":{"angle":360,"enabled":false,"range":0,"brightness":1,"color":null,"attenuation":0.1,"saturation":0,"contrast":0,"visionMode":"basic"},"detectionModes":[]},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145221566,"modifiedTime":1