:{"warlock":{"—":"—","Blunt":"Blunt","Bow":"Bow","Brawling":"Brawling","Crossbow":"Crossbow","Large blade":"Large blade","Pole arm":"Pole arm","Small blade":"Small blade","Thrown":"Thrown"},"warpstar":{"—":"—","Blades":"Blades","Blunt":"Blunt","Brawling":"Brawling","Ship gunner":"Ship gunner","Small arms":"Small arms","Thrown":"Thrown"}}},"activeSystem":"warlock"},"ownership":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}},{"_id":"jsHVFZuGIhpUxR9Q","name":"Hide","type":"Armour","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"","isEquipped":true,"type":{"value":"","choices":{"":"","Light":"Light","Modest":"Modest","Heavy":"Heavy"}},"reductionRoll":"1d3"},"ownership":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}},{"_id":"3O5pRxHOKXGsDE7h","name":"Poisonous","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":"jZ1bx1OgshF0koNu","sort":800000,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.56fsf7S8NIppsAj2"}},"system":{"description":"<p>This creature carries a poison or can inject a venom. If it successfully hits a target, the victim must test their luck. If they fail, the victim is poisoned, and loses [[/roll 1d6]] stamina at the start of the next [[/roll 1d3]] rounds. Poison or venom effects from the same source are not cumulative, although of course the creature can still inflict its normal damage when it hits.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.warlock.bestiary-warlock.GTUSNOLiCJJxCvZt"}},"system":{"resources":{"actionsPerRound":{"value":2,"max":2},"stamina":{"value":42,"max":42}},"biography":{"description":"<p>A bizarre combination of creatures, the chimera has the body of a lion, the tail of a scorpion and the heads of a dragon, a lion and a goat. It is a magical creature, created by ancient warlocks as a beast of war. Its nature is aggressive as it is full of pain, its body rebelling against the sorceries that hold it together. The scorpion tail and claws of the chimera drip an acidic venom, making areas it passes through smoke and reek.</p>"},"type":"Monster","weaponSkill":7,"adventuringSkills":5,"gear":{"weapons":[],"armour":[],"equipment":[]}},"ownership":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"prototypeToken":{"name":"Chimera","displayName":0,"actorLink":false,"width":1,"height":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"alpha":1,"light":{"alpha":0.5,"angle":360,"bright":0,"coloration":1,"dim":0,"luminosity":0.5,"saturation":0,"contrast":0,"shadows":0,"animation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5,"reverse":false,"type":null},"darkness":{"min":0,"max":1},"attenuation":0.5,"color":null},"disposition":-1,"displayBars":0,"bar1":{"attribute":null},"bar2":{"attribute":null},"flags":{},"randomImg":false,"texture":{"src":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/griffin-symbol.svg","scaleX":1,"scaleY":1,"offsetX":0,"offsetY":0,"rotation":0,"tint":null},"sight":{"angle":360,"enabled":false,"range":0,"brightness":1,"color":null,"attenuation":0.1,"saturation":0,"contrast":0,"visionMode":"basic"},"detectionModes":[]},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145221582,"modifiedTime":1662411890766,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"HXCJhlWq3JrUEVoM","name":"Ooze","type":"Monster","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/monsters/slime.svg","items":[{"_id":"SICl5EsFJuyd0gMw","name":"Engulf","type":"Weapon","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"","isEquipped":true,"type":{"value":"—","choices":{"warlock":{"":"","Casual":"Casual","Martial":"Martial"},"warpstar":{"":"","Small":"Small","Medium":"Medium","Heavy":"Heavy"}}},"damage":{"roll":"2d6","type":{"value":"Blast","choices":{"warlock":{"":"","Crushing":"Crushing","Piercing":"Piercing","Slashing":"Slashing","Blast":"Blast"},"warpstar":{"":"","Crushing":"Crushing","Piercing":"Piercing","Slashing":"Slashing","Energy":"Energy","Ship":"Ship"}}}},"skill":{"value":"Weapon Skill","choices":{"warlock":{"—":"—","Blunt":"Blunt","Bow":"Bow","Brawling":"Brawling","Crossbow":"Crossbow","Large blade":"Large blade","Pole arm":"Pole arm","Small blade":"Small blade","Thrown":"Thrown"},"warpstar":{"—":"—","Blades":"Blades","Blunt":"Blunt","Brawling":"Brawling","Ship gunner":"Ship gunner","Small arms":"Small arms","Thrown":"Thrown"}}},"activeSystem":"warlock"},"ownership":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}},{"_id":"vprq3vL1FFNPCrxJ","name":"Formless","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":"jZ1bx1OgshF0koNu","sort":600000,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.UHb3vwM1JEJWJ7fl"}},"system":{"description":"<p>The body of this creature has no real form, so it may slide under doors, squeeze through narrow spaces etc. as if it were a thick, viscous liquid.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}},{"_id":"edZ3oq9hfUsA9qo7","name":"Dissolve","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":"jZ1bx1OgshF0koNu","sort":200000,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.YOeq0X3kQBWDsJdw"}},"system":{"description":"<p>This being is able to dissolve matter. Any time it is successfully struck the attacker must test their luck. On a fail, their weapon is destroyed.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.warlock.bestiary-warlock.HXCJhlWq3JrUEVoM"}},"system":{"resources":{"actionsPerRound":{"value":2,"max":2},"stamina":{"value":35,"max":35}},"biography":{"description":"<p>Mindless and formless, the acidic ooze slides along the ground, dissolving anything organic it encounters, along with metals and pretty much everything else. They are easily avoided if seen, but can be extremely dangerous if they corner you or are encountered underwater, and can be very hard to kill.</p>"},"type":"Monster","weaponSkill":5,"adventuringSkills":0,"gear":{"weapons":[],"armour":[],"equipment":[]}},"ownership":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"prototypeToken":{"name":"Ooze","displayName":0,"actorLink":false,"width":1,"height":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"alpha":1,"light":{"alpha":0.5,"angle":360,"bright":0,"coloration":1,"dim":0,"luminosity":0.5,"saturation":0,"contrast":0,"shadows":0,"animation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5,"reverse":false,"type":null},"darkness":{"min":0,"max":1},"attenuation":0.5,"color":null},"disposition":-1,"displayBars":0,"bar1":{"attribute":null},"bar2":{"attribute":null},"flags":{},"randomImg":false,"texture":{"src":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/monsters/slime.svg","scaleX":1,"scaleY":1,"offsetX":0,"offsetY":0,"rotation":0,"tint":null},"sight":{"angle":360,"enabled":false,"range":0,"brightness":1,"color":null,"attenuation":0.1,"saturation":0,"contrast":0,"visionMode":"basic"},"detectionModes":[]},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145221595,"modifiedTime":1662411890767,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"I4iULjyZwj68Sgu6","name":"Goblin","type":"Monster","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/monsters/goblin-head.svg","items":[{"_id":"G4sQiqRwRJ0SZqjP","name":"Intelligent","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":"jZ1bx1OgshF0koNu","sort":700000,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.viEhV1k2WBxXnAHV"}},"system":{"description":"<p>This being is intelligent, can speak (but perhaps not in a tongue the characters know) and use tools and weapons. It is also able to create strategies and plans.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.warlock.bestiary-warlock.I4iULjyZwj68Sgu6"}},"system":{"resources":{"actionsPerRound":{"value":1,"max":1},"stamina":{"value":10,"max":10}},"biography":{"description":"<p>Some goblins are as tall as men but have a stooped posture which makes them look considerably smaller, others stand upright but are shorter in stature. They are skinny and ragged, with long arms and legs. Their faces are sharp, angular and frowning - goblins rarely look happy. They are not innately evil, but they are capricious, fickle, inquisitive and cunning. They can be cruel; as they truly believe that might is right - the biggest and strongest has the right to rule over the rest. They would be more dangerous, but they tend to have short attention spans and find it difficult sticking to one task. Only when pressed into the service of a greater, more calculating power such as the Warlock can they be a threat to human society.</p>\n<p>Goblins make their own weapons and armour, and are sometimes found in civilised lands where they are tolerated more than trusted. Their own kingdoms tend to be underground, as they have a natural affinity for the darkness and can see in dark as well as by day.</p>"},"type":"Uncivilised","weaponSkill":6,"adventuringSkills":4,"gear":{"weapons":[],"armour":[],"equipment":[]}},"ownership":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"prototypeToken":{"name":"Goblin","displayName":0,"actorLink":false,"width":1,"height":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"alpha":1,"light":{"alpha":0.5,"angle":360,"bright":0,"coloration":1,"dim":0,"luminosity":0.5,"saturation":0,"contrast":0,"shadows":0,"animation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5,"reverse":false,"type":null},"darkness":{"min":0,"max":1},"attenuation":0.5,"color":null},"disposition":-1,"displayBars":0,"bar1":{"attribute":null},"bar2":{"attribute":null},"flags":{},"randomImg":false,"texture":{"src":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/monsters/goblin-head.svg","scaleX":1,"scaleY":1,"offsetX":0,"offsetY":0,"rotation":0,"tint":null},"sight":{"angle":360,"enabled":false,"range":0,"brightness":1,"color":null,"attenuation":0.1,"saturation":0,"contrast":0,"visionMode":"basic"},"detectionModes":[]},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145221612,"modifiedTime":1662411890768,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"IOw7RP7L6gGI3Ntf","name":"Ghoul","type":"Monster","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/monsters/shambling-zombie.svg","items":[{"_id":"v5PEFQSnWhB3MqlZ","name":"Claw","type":"Weapon","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"","isEquipped":true,"type":{"value":"—","choices":{"warlock":{"":"","Casual":"Casual","Martial":"Martial"},"warpstar":{"":"","Small":"Small","Medium":"Medium","Heavy":"Heavy"}}},"damage":{"roll":"2d6","type":{"value":"Slashing","choices":{"warlock":{"":"","Crushing":"Crushing","Piercing":"Piercing","Slashing":"Slashing","Blast":"Blast"},"warpstar":{"":"","Crushing":"Crushing","Piercing":"Piercing","Slashing":"Slashing","Energy":"Energy","Ship":"Ship"}}}},"skill":{"value":"Weapon Skill","choices":{"warlock":{"—":"—","Blunt":"Blunt","Bow":"Bow","Brawling":"Brawling","Crossbow":"Crossbow","Large blade":"Large blade","Pole arm":"Pole arm","Small blade":"Small blade","Thrown":"Thrown"},"warpstar":{"—":"—","Blades":"Blades","Blunt":"Blunt","Brawling":"Brawling","Ship gunner":"Ship gunner","Small arms":"Small arms","Thrown":"Thrown"}}},"activeSystem":"warlock"},"ownership":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}},{"_id":"B4Bdci3VXqOvEc3A","name":"Hide","type":"Armour","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"","isEquipped":false,"type":{"value":"","choices":{"":"","Light":"Light","Modest":"Modest","Heavy":"Heavy"}},"reductionRoll":"1d3"},"ownership":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}},{"_id":"ZSwWy0wpCUvplMKx","name":"Poisonous","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":"jZ1bx1OgshF0koNu","sort":800000,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.56fsf7S8NIppsAj2"}},"system":{"description":"<p>This creature carries a poison or can inject a venom. If it successfully hits a target, the victim must test their luck. If they fail, the victim is poisoned, and loses [[/roll 1d6]] stamina at the start of the next [[/roll 1d3]] rounds. Poison or venom effects from the same source are not cumulative, although of course the creature can still inflict its normal damage when it hits.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.warlock.bestiary-warlock.IOw7RP7L6gGI3Ntf"}},"system":{"resources":{"actionsPerRound":{"value":2,"max":2},"stamina":{"value":18,"max":18}},"biography":{"description":"<p>Foul beings that feed on the dead, some say that ghouls were once humans who were twisted by a terrible spell. Whatever their origin, these disease-ridden beings haunt graveyards and other tombs in search of corpses to consume. Some say that dead bodies are a kind of drug to ghouls, who experience the lives of those they consume, but this cannot be confirmed. All that is known is their terrible, terrible hunger for flesh.</p>"},"type":"Monster","weaponSkill":7,"adventuringSkills":5,"gear":{"weapons":[],"armour":[],"equipment":[]}},"ownership":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"prototypeToken":{"name":"Ghoul","displayName":0,"actorLink":false,"width":1,"height":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"alpha":1,"light":{"alpha":0.5,"angle":360,"bright":0,"coloration":1,"dim":0,"luminosity":0.5,"saturation":0,"contrast":0,"shadows":0,"animation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5,"reverse":false,"type":null},"darkness":{"min":0,"max":1},"attenuation":0.5,"color":null},"disposition":-1,"displayBars":0,"bar1":{"attribute":null},"bar2":{"attribute":null},"flags":{},"randomImg":false,"texture":{"src":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/monsters/shambling-zombie.svg","scaleX":1,"scaleY":1,"offsetX":0,"offsetY":0,"rotation":0,"tint":null},"sight":{"angle":360,"enabled":false,"range":0,"brightness":1,"color":null,"attenuation":0.1,"saturation":0,"contrast":0,"visionMode":"basic"},"detectionModes":[]},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145221629,"modifiedTime":1662411890769,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"JkiK1NJQXTUyL4gw","name":"Unman","type":"Monster","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/monsters/werewolf.svg","items":[{"_id":"hLOpCJGueqGfU3mo","name":"Intelligent","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":"jZ1bx1OgshF0koNu","sort":700000,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.viEhV1k2WBxXnAHV"}},"system":{"description":"<p>This being is intelligent, can speak (but perhaps not in a tongue the characters know) and use tools and weapons. It is also able to create strategies and plans.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.warlock.bestiary-warlock.JkiK1NJQXTUyL4gw"}},"system":{"resources":{"actionsPerRound":{"value":1,"max":1},"stamina":{"value":15,"max":15}},"biography":{"description":"<p>Unmen are humans mixed bizarrely with beasts, often with animal heads and limbs. They are exclusively the creation of foul magics, and display a terrible anger at their twisted nature. They lurk in deep forests and make the roads a danger to all.</p>"},"type":"Civilised","weaponSkill":5,"adventuringSkills":4,"gear":{"weapons":[],"armour":[],"equipment":[]}},"ownership":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"prototypeToken":{"name":"Unman","displayName":0,"actorLink":false,"width":1,"height":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"alpha":1,"light":{"alpha":0.5,"angle":360,"bright":0,"coloration":1,"dim":0,"luminosity":0.5,"saturation":0,"contrast":0,"shadows":0,"animation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5,"reverse":false,"type":null},"darkness":{"min":0,"max":1},"attenuation":0.5,"color":null},"disposition":-1,"displayBars":0,"bar1":{"attribute":null},"bar2":{"attribute":null},"flags":{},"randomImg":false,"texture":{"src":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/monsters/werewolf.svg","scaleX":1,"scaleY":1,"offsetX":0,"offsetY":0,"rotation":0,"tint":null},"sigh