HV"}},"system":{"description":"<p>This being is intelligent, can speak (but perhaps not in a tongue the characters know) and use tools and weapons. It is also able to create strategies and plans.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}},{"_id":"MGrXXBnnTQP48gN3","name":"Spell caster","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":"jZ1bx1OgshF0koNu","sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.FOVCFt6tZfXWVBEK"}},"system":{"description":"<p>The being is able to cast spells. The games master should feel free to assign the creature spells that reflect its power. It uses stamina to cast spells and requires an incantation skill check.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.warlock.bestiary-warlock.2DrYWx0Jt6E98GBF"}},"system":{"resources":{"actionsPerRound":{"value":2,"max":2},"stamina":{"value":43,"max":43}},"biography":{"description":"<p>The great treemen are found in the deepest woods, where they protect their woodland realm with a passion that quickly turns to anger should they be aroused. Allies of the elves, who also recognise the beauty of the forests, treemen are able to pull down buildings with their root-like grasp when driven into a rage.</p>"},"type":"Monster","weaponSkill":9,"adventuringSkills":4,"gear":{"weapons":[],"armour":[],"equipment":[]}},"ownership":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"prototypeToken":{"name":"Treeman","displayName":0,"actorLink":false,"width":1,"height":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"alpha":1,"light":{"alpha":0.5,"angle":360,"bright":0,"coloration":1,"dim":0,"luminosity":0.5,"saturation":0,"contrast":0,"shadows":0,"animation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5,"r